        {
          "type": "article",
          "title": "Color palette",
          "modules": [
            {
              "type": "module",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "module-body",
                  "html": "<p>This color palette comprises primary and accent colors that can be used for illustration or to develop your brand colors. They&#x2019;ve been designed to work harmoniously with each other.</p><p>The color palette starts with primary colors and fills in the spectrum to create a complete and usable palette for Android, Web, and iOS. Google suggests using the 500 colors as the primary colors in your app and the other colors as accents colors. </p>"
                }
              ]
